will account for layout-generated components like splitters and should be used
instead of index based <a href='#!/api/Ext.ux.colorpick.Slider-method-move'>method-move</a>. If `before` is <a href='#!/api/null'>null</a> then the
`item` will be the last item in this container.

    var tb = Ext.create({
